Didier Stevens — 1768.py
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Description : Cobalt Strike beacon configuration analyser
  Author      : Didier Stevens <https://blog.didierstevens.com/>
  URL         : https://github.com/DidierStevens/DidierStevensSuite
  License     : Public Domain
                "Source code put in the public domain by Didier Stevens,
                 no Copyright"

  Used in     : dumpex/hunt/cs_beacon.py
                rules/yara/cs_indicators.yar (CS_Beacon_Config_XOR69,
                CS_Beacon_Config_XOR2E)
  Used in     : dumpex/hunt/encoding.py (Layer 0 — _scan_sleep_mask and helpers)
                [cs-analyze-processdump.py and 1768.py]

  Nature of use:
    The beacon config detection algorithm, TLV field parser, Malleable C2 instruction decoder, config field identifier table, beacon/proxy type lookup tables, CS version estimator, and config sanity check logic in cs_beacon.py are adapted from the corresponding functions in 1768.py. The XOR-encoded signature byte patterns in cs_indicators.yar are derived from the same work.


